Package: collatzR
Type: Package
Title: Package for implementing Collatz Conjucture 
Version: 1.0.0.0
Date: 2023-09-24
Authors@R: 
    person("Sulman", "Owili", , "s.owili@cgiar.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7401-5326"))
Author: Sulman Owili [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sulman Owili <s.owili@cgiar.org>
Description: A package for exploring and visualizing the Collatz conjecture, a fascinating mathematical sequence. It provides functions for: (1) determining if a number is even or odd, (2) performing the Collatz operation on the selected number, (3) generating Collatz sequences for various starting numbers, and visualizing the seguence for the selected number.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: knitr, xfun
